<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contract Notification</title>

    <style>
        /* Background image */
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: "Segoe UI", Arial, sans-serif;
            background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507525428034-b723cf961d3e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1600&q=80') no-repeat center center fixed;
            background-size: cover;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        /* Dark overlay for better readability */
        body::before {
            content: "";
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
            z-index: 0;
        }

        .card {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            background: #ffffff;
            max-width: 550px;
            width: 90%;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 18px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease;
        }

        h1 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #0d9488;
            font-size: 28px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        p {
            color: #555;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .info-box {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            background: #eef4ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #0d9488;
            padding: 15px 18px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-top: 18px;
            color: #333;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .info-column {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 200px;
        }

        .info-column strong {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #0d9488;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .contract-btn {
            margin-top: 25px;
            width: 100%;
            display: inline-block;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 12px 0;
            background: #0d9488;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: 0.2s;
        }

        .contract-btn:hover {
            background: #0f766e;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(10px);
            }

            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="card">
        <h1>You Have a Contract to Sign ✍️</h1>

        <p>Please review the contract details and proceed to sign it.</p>

        <div class="info-box">
            <div class="info-column">
                <strong>Contract Information</strong>
                <p>Contract ID: <b><%= locals.data.contract.bookingId %></b></p>
                <p>Created on: <%= locals.data.contract.createdAt %></p>
                <p>Status: Pending Signature</p>
            </div>

            <div class="info-column">
                <strong>User Information</strong>
                <p>Name: <b><%= locals.data.user.name %></b></p>
                <p>Email: <%= locals.data.user.email %></p>
                <p>Phone: <%= locals.data.user.phone %></p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <a class="contract-btn" href="<%= locals.data.host %>/contracts">Go to Contract Page</a>
    </div>
</body>

</html>